{"tid":630880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要做賤種？ 巴閉囉 英雄主義囉 黑哨囉","createTime":"2018-04-16T03:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T11:10:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd58f74bbdf96f0dec2b6186f2fa179d4c7c2f29","tid":630880,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"我波台唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以𢱕你。<br />\n𡃁仔你係疤狗呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過黑哨未呀？你見過完場前十二碼未呀？<br />\n你話賤種朗你偶像吖嘛，你見過賤種朗未呀？<br />\n賤種蝗揸fit人吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知佢佢要靠黑哨 球王先做到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢個仔，無老母，佢救唔到。<br />\n你知唔知賤種朗 諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢好想繼續做賤種蝗揸fit人，<br />\n佢因爲有黑哨唔會離開賤種蝗，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，賤種朗讀唔讀書，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，行錯路，冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"11f9e601e44ddf2f95d7f9bccb07f813d0654d83","tid":630880,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b0e3d3addd63a61a7974ea54c064b201738584","tid":630880,"uid":9708,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"改野都俾d深度啊 問疤狗見過黑哨未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797600d3c774acd504f4828ec430672253f12b3b","tid":630880,"uid":74751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04b0e3d3addd63a61a7974ea54c064b201738584","tid":630880,"uid":9708,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"改野都俾d深度啊 問疤狗見過黑哨未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de2e5ae7e3568c598f20e3fdb524ed4ead6e035","tid":630880,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f9e601e44